time complexity: O(n log n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Iterates through numbers from 1 to num, calculates the digit sum of each number, and counts those with even digit sums. The solution is efficient due to its simplicity and lack of unnecessary computations.
